Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:55.94,Episode,,0,0,0,,{\fade(640,640)\pos(975,722)}Episode 7
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.69,0:02:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,please don’t risk swallowing the Heavenly Flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.26,0:02:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were to fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.26,0:02:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,please forget about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You bunch of fellows,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,do you really think I wouldn’t kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dare I ask Sect Leader Yun, so brazenly barging into my Snake People tribe,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,why you not only lack the slightest apology
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but are instead this arrogant?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.93,0:04:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that you think my clan can be bullied?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This time I was entrusted by Gu He to help exchange for the Heavenly Flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not intend to harm people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, you don’t know good intentions from bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I change my mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,leave at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t speak too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be a Fight Emperor,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but trying to face us five Fight Kings
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:05:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,isn’t going to be an easy task!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You can try.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.50,0:05:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A Fight Emperor’s strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,could a Fight King shake it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.02,0:05:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Her speed is too quick,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,don’t take her on alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare the seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.18,0:06:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Five Snake Spirit Gathering!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Snake People’s fusion Fight Technique;
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,turns out it really is something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Five Snake Poison Killing Seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yun Zhi, this girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I reckon she really does have ways to let you become a strong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you’re mad again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saved her in the Magical Beast Mountain Range,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew she was kind hearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.42,0:06:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Before leaving,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:06:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,she even left behind the Sea Core Vest for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Alas,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,she doesn’t know
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,how important the Heavenly Flame is to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.14,0:07:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl has a good heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but she doesn’t know,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.37,0:07:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,for the sake of revenge, of shame,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,just how much you’ve sacrificed during these three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.38,0:07:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,find a safe place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to swallow the Heavenly Flame as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.58,0:07:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Snake People practitioners have caught up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s the place we just left from;
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yun Zhi, she—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I sense the auras of five Snake People Fight Kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1072)}This light pillar seems to be the Snake People displaying their fusion Fight Technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.74,0:07:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Fusion Fight Technique?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yun Zhi, this girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I presume even she would find it tricky to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.86,0:07:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,let’s quickly hide the Heavenly Flame
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:07:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and then go help Yun Zhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A portal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s a powerful and terrifying aura inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I am actually unable to perceive this giant snake’s rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot let this beast channel out of the void.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.74,0:09:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wind’s Peak,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.68,0:09:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Killer Meteor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We sacrificed our lifespan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and used the Five Snake Poison Killing Seal to summon the Spirit Snake;
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,we will be sure to leave your soul in the desert!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.57,0:09:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Finish her off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.74,0:09:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wind’s Peak,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:09:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Setting Sun Flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.54,0:10:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.62,0:10:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Spirit Snake isn’t a body of flesh and blood;
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,even a Fight Emperor shouldn’t think of hurting the Spirit Snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The disgrace suffered by the Snake People,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,only blood can wash it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn’t expect
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.84,0:11:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,that I would actually fall here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Another Fight Emperor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.49,0:12:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This flame
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.42,0:12:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,is actually a Heavenly Flame?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.14,0:12:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You are gravely injured,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,need to heal your wounds immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you Fight Emperor, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.85,0:12:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask for honorable sir’s name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.73,0:12:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The favor of saving my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.78,0:12:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I will definitely repay it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just asked by someone to come help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.78,0:12:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Asked by someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not know who requested that you save me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,could it be
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.29,0:12:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Gu He?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Gu He doesn’t have the qualification to move me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.73,0:12:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly heal up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.62,0:13:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight Emperor, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,if you leave now
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you would become the Snake People frien—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you who hurt her;
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,then leave your lives behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.14,0:13:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1072)}This Fight Emperor’s Heavenly Flame just so happens to restrain the flame Spirit Snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Overreaching beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.46,0:14:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,this Heavenly Flame...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.18,0:14:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There was not half a grudge between the Snake People and sir;
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.69,0:14:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,sir’s manner today,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.54,0:14:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,we will firmly remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.01,0:14:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Snake Technique: Split!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.70,0:14:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t allow the tiger to return to the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we’ve become enemies,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.79,0:14:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,definitely can’t leave behind seeds of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But Teacher—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Little fellow,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,she should be alright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t know how to face her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Matters of emotion,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the old me can’t help you with.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Snake People have already fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you are alright,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,then till we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.74,0:16:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Many thanks to sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I still do not know
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,who was it that asked you to come help?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a little fellow who requested that I come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me, on his behalf, to say sorry to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.54,0:16:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He may have gone a bit overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Little fellow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,could it be
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yao Yan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask the old sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,he and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.85,0:16:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,can we meet again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.98,0:16:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yun Zhi gazed in the direction Yao Yan departed from,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting for that man
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.11,0:17:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to once again appear before her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Yao Yan at that time
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,would also be the Three Year Agreement’s attendee,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,an encounter is fated,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.54,0:17:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but it is also damned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.02,0:17:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,what is predestined
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,is also inescapable doom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,When these two appear on the same person,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.70,0:17:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that person,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.70,0:17:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,as your destined one,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.10,0:17:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,they are also
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,your inescapable
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,doom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Her Majesty The Queen may not have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,why do you say this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.41,0:17:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just then, when the Fight Emperor was about to kill us off,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I detected a thread of the Queen’s aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.33,0:18:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it was Her Majesty The Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Her Majesty The Queen,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.98,0:18:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,just where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I am unable to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.05,0:18:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,One day
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Her Majesty The Queen will return.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.94,0:18:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.54,0:19:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,first pull over the Heavenly Flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then have your palm reach into the Heavenly Flame;
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,find the flame seed at its core;
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and take it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No way,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,putting my hand into the Heavenly Flame?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn’t that looking to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.93,0:19:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,With the Blood Lotus Pill’s blood film,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.66,0:19:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,there won’t be any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.90,0:19:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,come over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.38,0:19:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The Three Year Agreement is almost here;
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,refining the Heavenly Flame
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is imperative!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What terrifying destructive power;
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.68,0:19:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,after not even an hour, this temperature
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,could cause a large city
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to be burnt to ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:19:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:19:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I must catch and take you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Caught you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the flame seed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A thousand years of absorbed energy is compressed within the flame seed;
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,if the flame seed were to completely erupt
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,even a Fight Ancestor,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,when facing such catastrophic power
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.98,0:20:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,would have only one ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That is
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.93,0:20:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,their demise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.66,0:20:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Swallow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.81,0:20:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.54,0:20:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you’re not giving up,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,then hold on to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.82,0:20:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Life or death,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,strong or weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.49,0:20:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Your choice begins from this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.10,0:20:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.24,0:21:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m going to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.98,0:21:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly consume the Ice Spirit Cold Fountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Drive it to circulate through the meridians in your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,After completing the circulation,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.38,0:21:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,use your Dou Qi to enwrap the Heavenly Flame,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,direct it along the route of the Flame Mantra Qi Method,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and then swallow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.94,0:21:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.69,0:21:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,stabilize your mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.58,0:21:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you cannot allow the flame seed to come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.02,0:21:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If the flame seed leaves your body,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.11,0:21:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it would mean swallowing the Heavenly Flame had failed,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.78,0:21:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and you would also be burnt to ashes by the flame!
